was the best cure.

485
00:24:41,706 --> 00:24:44,080
It will heal you.
Isn't that right, Lily?

486
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:45,640
Really?

487
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:48,159
Think she's telling the truth, Cod?

488
00:24:48,523 --> 00:24:50,078
Yeah. Too bad too,

489
00:24:50,237 --> 00:24:52,263
'cause the jealous, crazy lady
that kills her sister

490
00:24:52,303 --> 00:24:55,101
to be with the himbo brother-in-law
is always a welcome rest stop...

491
00:24:55,333 --> 00:24:56,730
