501
00:25:23,650 --> 00:25:25,532
Very well. Now for the big news.

502
00:25:26,193 --> 00:25:29,483
The <i>Darling Mermaid Darlings</i>...
have picked up a third.

503
00:25:30,713 --> 00:25:32,120
What?

504
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:34,150
- That was faked surprise.
- Yeah, it was.

505
00:25:34,190 --> 00:25:36,520
Olive's been keeping me
informed on the Charles sister.

506
00:25:36,601 --> 00:25:39,485
- How are they getting along?
- Vivian's her usual, sweet self.

507
00:25:39,525 --> 00:25:42,139
Lily seems cautious,
but still professional.

508
00:25:42,179 --> 00:25:43,976
And Coral is thrilled to have a job

509
00:25:44,016 --> 00:25:46,200
