first professional appearance in years.

519
00:26:07,416 --> 00:26:09,827
There's no way you can miss it,
especially now.

520
00:26:09,867 --> 00:26:11,330
Here's the really...

521
00:26:11,528 --> 00:26:14,760
juicy secret that not even
Olive Snook the spy knows.

522
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:18,120
